com.myronmarston.music.settings
Class Section

java.lang.Object
  com.myronmarston.music.settings.AbstractVoiceOrSection
      com.myronmarston.music.settings.Section

public class Section
extends AbstractVoiceOrSection

The entire fractal piece is composed of a series of sections. Each section represents a group of bars of the piece of music, e.g., bars 8-15. The section is responsible to make sure each voice in this section is the same length.
